cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and the response of a deep neural network to a visual illusion. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper discusses the neural network's behavior and its potential as a model for human perception, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the non-monotonic response of the neural network, which could be relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
